; Test case for issue #2297
; The account_total expression returns the per-account running balance
; instead of the global running total across all accounts.
;
; Without account_total, `reg` shows the global running total which
; resets to zero at the end of each balanced transaction.
; With -T account_total, each posting shows the cumulative balance
; for that specific account across all transactions.

2024/01/01 Opening Balance
    Assets:Checking    $1000.00
    Equity:Opening Balances

2024/01/05 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/10 More Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg -T account_total
24-Jan-01 Opening Balance       Assets:Checking            $1000.00     $1000.00
                                Equit:Opening Balances    $-1000.00    $-1000.00
24-Jan-05 Grocery Store         Expenses:Food               $100.00      $100.00
                                Assets:Checking            $-100.00      $900.00
24-Jan-10 More Groceries        Expenses:Food                $50.00      $150.00
                                Assets:Checking             $-50.00      $850.00
end test
